<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لمَّا نَظرْتُ إِلَى الفِرنْدِ بصَفْحِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَبْصَرْتُهُ بِدَمِ القُلُوبِ خَضِيبَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَرَمَى عَنِ اللَّحْظِ العَلِيلِ إِلَى الحَشَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَهْمَ المَنُونِ فَكَانَ فيهِ مُصِيبَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>هَلَاّ سَأَلْتَ لِحَاظَهُ يَوْمَ النَّوَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هَلْ غَادَرَتْ لَكَ فِي الحَيَاةِ نَصِيبَا ...<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>